title: Hickok Aluminum Handle Bypass Tree Loppers Made in USA (36)
description: Our tree loppers are commercial grade pruning tools designed for making large cuts (up to 2"). The fine hickory or aluminum alloy handles offer a cushioned response to the cutting action, and are available in a variety of lengths. Made in the USA, these tree loppers are made of the very highest quality, are as much as 30 percent lighter than comparable loppers, and are designed for professionals making thousands of cuts every season.
